-- U.S. Open Says Play to Resume at 12:10 P.M. at Merion Golf Club
-- B y   E r i k   M a t u s z e w s k i
-- 2013-06-13T15:18:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-06-13/u-s-open-says-play-to-resume-at-12-10-p-m-at-merion-golf-club.html
Golf at the U.S. Open will resume at
12:10 p.m. after stormy weather forced the U.S. Golf Association
to suspend play at 8:36 a.m.  Afternoon tee times at Merion Golf Club in Ardmore,
Pennsylvania, will be delayed three hours, 34 minutes, the USGA
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Erik Matuszewski in  New York  at 
 matuszewski@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
